tor $M/R$ of the star as already found in previous studies in\nwhich the slow rotation approximation has been used. Here $M$ and $R$ denote\nthe mass and radius of the star, respectively.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 11 Jun 2004 06:34:24 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 25 Dec 2004 03:43:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-10"}
