anies angular momentum-flux unless the flux is an s-wave.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 11 Jun 2004 07:44:40 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 1 Nov 2004 07:44:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-10"}
