e internally\nconsistent with the governing equation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 11 Jun 2004 02:36:59 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 11 Oct 2004 18:39:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2007-05-23"}
